text: Andrew Rasemene (born 25 March 1995) is a South African cricketer. Rasemene made his first-class debut for the Northerns against Gauteng He made his List A debut for Northerns against North West on 13 December 2015.name="Match"> In September 2019, he was named in Limpopo's squad for the 2019–20 CSA Provincial T20 Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Northerns cricketers Category:Free State cricketers
